KCCAns: For banana, a dose of 200:300 g of NK/plant is applied throughout the cropping period through split application and phosphorus alone is applied as basal dose at the time of planting. Water requirement -  25 lit per plant (normal density); 40 lit per plant (2 suckers / pit); 50 lit per pit (3 suckers/pit).
